{"tid":195814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夫被中國扣押 赴京尋夫被阻 李：若有自由 沒有尊嚴與狗有何差異","createTime":"2017-04-11T01:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T01:44:06.000Z","uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48deee1f129de4d1dd0d2e8c92c3ff0fa371a930","tid":195814,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20170411/37613390/?utm_source=Line&amp;utm_medium=iOS_Share&amp;utm_campaign=%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%93%B2%E5%A6%BB%EF%BC%9A%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%B7%9F%E5%BC%B7%E6%AC%8A%E5%93%80%E6%B1%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Fappledaily%2Farticle%2Fheadline%2F20170411%2F37613390%2F%3Futm_source%3DLine%26utm_medium%3DiOS_Share%26utm_campaign%3D%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2593%25B2%25E5%25A6%25BB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B7%259F%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2593%2580%25E6%25B1%2582&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4e9a940d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20170411/37613390/?utm_source=Line&amp;utm_medium=iOS_Share&amp;utm_campaign=%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%93%B2%E5%A6%BB%EF%BC%9A%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%B7%9F%E5%BC%B7%E6%AC%8A%E5%93%80%E6%B1%82</a>"},{"pid":"fa3512e2bc263e13b7b337d45a31589663d6296b","tid":195814,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"灣民進黨前黨工李明哲遭大陸以「涉嫌危害國家安全」為由於上月底拘留調查後，李明哲妻子李凈瑜原訂昨日坐飛機赴大陸「救夫」，但台胞證卻遭註銷，計劃受阻。大陸方面昨日通過中間人將李明哲親筆信交給李家。國台辦事前曾表示，台灣一些別有用心的組織和人士蓄意造謠生事，企圖藉此對大陸方面惡意攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n李凈瑜原定昨日中午一時搭乘中國國際航空班機赴北京尋夫，但抵達桃園機場後，卻被告知台胞證等證件已被大陸方面註銷。中央社報道，李凈瑜直呼很震驚、難過，並搭乘捷運返家。三立新聞網則稱，李凈瑜表示，此行是希望拜訪國台辦、檢察院等單位，「去北京不是去鬧事，而是去救人」，希望能了解李明哲下落及被拘押理由，確認他的身體健康。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚李凈瑜發出公開信表示，她不會讓李明哲為了獲得自由而失去尊嚴，大陸再強大，「只能剝奪我們的生命與自由，但絕對粉碎不了我們的尊嚴」。李凈瑜又表示，絕不跟強權哀求，「我必須戰鬥下去，我不會讓我先生為獲得自由而失去尊嚴，像狗一樣活未來的一生」。"},{"pid":"4974c260a2f9b0a4a948b0af721cc460f1b0f26d","tid":195814,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"都已經係中國人喇，仲講咩自袖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dc9e74cee5f968914e83aeeb82e011724dd373","tid":195814,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:28:55.000Z","msg":"好人好姐上大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2a83522f94d3132c6773e2c95bea39a0a83bce","tid":195814,"uid":75776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都已經係中國人喇，仲講咩自袖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非法逮捕都可以用族裔去合理化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你個腦係咪核裂變阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}